seo: PHPOK,前台无限制注入,漏洞检测,代码注入,高危漏洞
summary: 该插件用于检测PHPOK 5.3版本是否存在前台无限制注入漏洞，通过发送特定payload并验证响应来确认漏洞是否存在。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the PHPOK 5.3 version has an unrestricted injection vulnerability in the front-end. It confirms the existence of the vulnerability by sending a specific payload and verifying the response.
